org.imageterrier.locfile

Class PositionSpec

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.imageterrier.locfile.PositionSpec

  • public class PositionSpec
extends Object
    The PositionSpec class defines the type of position that will be stored in the payload of each term-document posting, together with the methods required for encoding and decoding this information.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare

      static class  PositionSpec.PositionSpecMode
